<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 02:34:04 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列部长们支持赋予议会权力挑选司法监察员的法案；总检察长反对</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-ministers-back-bill-giving-knesset-power-to-pick-judicial-ombudsman-ag-opposes/00000190-6a93-d90c-a7fc-7f9785f00000</link><description>该法案将让候选人由立法者以无记名投票的方式批准，而不是由司法任命委员会批准。法院管理顾问批评该法案，称其是“旨在削弱司法部门权力的政权更迭运动的一部分”</description><pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 19:50:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-ministers-back-bill-giving-knesset-power-to-pick-judicial-ombudsman-ag-opposes/00000190-6a93-d90c-a7fc-7f9785f00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列内阁批准更改农业部名称 可能耗资高达200万谢克尔</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/cabinet-approves-changing-agriculture-ministrys-name-may-cost-up-to-2-million-shekels/00000190-6a7a-d9ec-a19e-ef7f380b0000</link><description>在部长阿维·迪希特 (Avi Dichter) 要求更改后，该部现更名为农业和粮食安全部。以色列优质政府运动猛烈抨击了“投资数百万谢克尔进行无用的表面改变”的“妄想和不必要”的决定</description><pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 19:20:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/cabinet-approves-changing-agriculture-ministrys-name-may-cost-up-to-2-million-shekels/00000190-6a7a-d9ec-a19e-ef7f380b0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登的民意调查很糟糕，但内塔尼亚胡的民意调查更糟</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-30/ty-article/.highlight/bidens-polling-is-abysmal-but-netanyahus-is-even-worse/00000190-69a4-d9ec-a19e-efb59ab30000</link><description>在周四总统辩论后糟糕的民意调查结果中，美国总统乔·拜登可以稍稍安慰自己，因为至少有一位领导人更不被美国公民信任来领导他们</description><pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 19:04:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-30/ty-article/.highlight/bidens-polling-is-abysmal-but-netanyahus-is-even-worse/00000190-69a4-d9ec-a19e-efb59ab30000</guid></item><item><title>数千名极端正统以色列人抗议征兵；正统派部长的汽车被投掷石块</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/thousands-protest-against-haredi-conscription-ministers-car-pelted-with-stones/00000190-6a2d-d90c-a7fc-7f2de43a0000</link><description>数千名极端正统派男子涌上耶路撒冷街头，吹着号角，举着标语牌，反对高等法院的裁决，该裁决称他们必须应征入伍。 UTJ党部长Yitzchak Goldknopf开车穿过集会，抗议者向他的车投掷石块</description><pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 18:57:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/thousands-protest-against-haredi-conscription-ministers-car-pelted-with-stones/00000190-6a2d-d90c-a7fc-7f2de43a0000</guid></item><item><title>永远的新星节：以色列人跳舞纪念哈马斯的受害者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/nova-festival-is-back-israelis-dancing-with-tears-in-their-eyes-in-tel-aviv/00000190-6a34-d407-aff0-6f3e057d0000</link><description>10月7日诺瓦节大屠杀受害者的感人音乐会一半是纪念一半是电子舞会</description><pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 18:19:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/nova-festival-is-back-israelis-dancing-with-tears-in-their-eyes-in-tel-aviv/00000190-6a34-d407-aff0-6f3e057d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 268 天：伊斯兰圣战组织称关键特工在西岸被以色列国防军杀害</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-268-islamic-jihad-says-key-operative-killed-by-idf-in-west-bank/00000190-6a0d-d01f-abbe-7f0d27360001</link><description>巴勒斯坦伊斯兰圣战组织表示，其一名关键成员在以色列无人机袭击约旦河西岸时丧生 ■ 以色列国防军提高了对参与 10 月 7 日大屠杀但不属于哈马斯或伊斯兰圣战组织成员的巴勒斯坦人进行定点暗杀的门槛 ■ 阿拉伯联盟不再将真主党列为恐怖组织 ■ 战争进入 268 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 16:54:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-268-islamic-jihad-says-key-operative-killed-by-idf-in-west-bank/00000190-6a0d-d01f-abbe-7f0d27360001</guid></item><item><title>以色列部长批准为非犹太人保留“行政拘留”的法律</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-ministers-approve-law-that-would-reserve-administrative-detention-for-non-jews/00000190-69d7-d407-aff0-6fdfaa740000</link><description>拟议的法律规定，只有当该人属于旨在摧毁国家或伤害其公民的“恐怖组织”时，才允许行政拘留或未经审判的拘留。 10 月 7 日至 5 月 1 日期间，有 10 名犹太人被行政拘留，而阿拉伯人则有 2,733 名</description><pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 16:53:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-ministers-approve-law-that-would-reserve-administrative-detention-for-non-jews/00000190-69d7-d407-aff0-6fdfaa740000</guid></item><item><title>以色列内阁批准在内盖夫建造极端正统城市的计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-cabinet-authorizes-plans-for-ultra-orthodox-city-to-be-built-in-negev/00000190-698d-d90c-a7fc-7f8d9c9e0000</link><description>这座名为 Tilah 的新城市将容纳约 80,000 名居民。尽管遭到财政部的反对，但该计划仍在推进，财政部称与现有城市的扩张相比成本过高。环保组织和内盖夫市政府也反对该计划</description><pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 16:45:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-cabinet-authorizes-plans-for-ultra-orthodox-city-to-be-built-in-negev/00000190-698d-d90c-a7fc-7f8d9c9e0000</guid></item><item><title>为了生存，以色列现在必须袭击伊朗</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-06-30/ty-article-opinion/.premium/to-survive-israel-must-strike-iran-now/00000190-69e8-d01f-abbe-7de8d2260000</link><description>如果以色列证明无法使用常规武器摧毁伊朗核项目，那么它可能别无选择，只能诉诸非常规能力</description><pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 16:31:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-06-30/ty-article-opinion/.premium/to-survive-israel-must-strike-iran-now/00000190-69e8-d01f-abbe-7de8d2260000</guid></item><item><title>以色列工党与左翼梅雷茨合并为一党，称为“民主党”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/israels-labor-party-left-wing-meretz-merge-to-be-called-the-democrats/00000190-69ec-d499-a5bf-e9febff20000</link><description>根据工党主席亚伊尔·戈兰和梅雷茨领导人托梅尔·雷兹尼克签署的协议，这不是技术性合并，而是创建一个全新的政党，该政党将作为一个单一实体继续前进</description><pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 16:15:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/israels-labor-party-left-wing-meretz-merge-to-be-called-the-democrats/00000190-69ec-d499-a5bf-e9febff20000</guid></item><item><title>拉宾暗杀喜剧和失控的阴茎吸引年轻的以色列人回到战时剧院</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/theater/2024-06-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/rabin-assassination-comedy-and-a-runaway-penis-lure-young-israelis-back-to-wartime-theater/00000190-59c5-d63a-a7b2-5ddf09e00000</link><description>特拉维夫卡梅里剧院的新一代剧团将幽默与震撼人心的内容结合在一起，并不回避政治主题。但加沙战争带来了不同的困境：导演说，外面的世界“太疯狂了，我们开始觉得我们的排练室是世界上唯一正常的地方”</description><pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 15:43:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/theater/2024-06-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/rabin-assassination-comedy-and-a-runaway-penis-lure-young-israelis-back-to-wartime-theater/00000190-59c5-d63a-a7b2-5ddf09e00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列消息人士称人质交易尚未完成，目标是回到谈判桌</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-source-says-hostage-deal-not-close-goal-is-to-get-back-to-negotiating-table/00000190-6942-d9ec-a19e-ef57f8cd0000</link><description>消息人士称，“双方之间的距离”很大，特别是在内塔尼亚胡发表有关“部分协议”的声明之后，而且调解员现在才试图重启谈判。另一位消息人士称，辛瓦尔对达成协议不感兴趣，他更希望北方局势升级而不是结束战争</description><pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 13:59:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-source-says-hostage-deal-not-close-goal-is-to-get-back-to-negotiating-table/00000190-6942-d9ec-a19e-ef57f8cd0000</guid></item><item><title>警察“掐住我的脖子，拉扯我的头发，踢我”：反政府集会上警察暴力激增，反对派 MK 遭到袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-violence-spikes-at-anti-govt-rallies-opposition-mk-also-bears-brunt/00000190-68e6-d90c-a7fc-7fe6e5950000</link><description>一名警察向一名抗议者吐口水，并威胁要“强奸他的母亲”。 ■ 反对派议员纳马·拉齐米 (Naama Lazimi) 在特拉维夫的抗议活动中被一名警察猛烈推搡。当警方指控拉齐米“利用议会豁免权”时，MK 回应道：“这是[本-格维尔]政权的警察”</description><pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 13:33:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-violence-spikes-at-anti-govt-rallies-opposition-mk-also-bears-brunt/00000190-68e6-d90c-a7fc-7fe6e5950000</guid></item><item><title>阿拉伯联盟高级官员表示，不再将真主党视为恐怖组织</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/arab-league-no-longer-views-hezbollah-as-terrorist-group-top-official-says/00000190-68ed-d747-add0-e8fd4a5e0000</link><description>阿拉伯联盟助理秘书长霍萨姆·扎基宣布对埃及媒体的政策转变</description><pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 11:59:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/arab-league-no-longer-views-hezbollah-as-terrorist-group-top-official-says/00000190-68ed-d747-add0-e8fd4a5e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府批准内塔尼亚胡新办公室和住所</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-could-get-two-new-residences-and-an-office-as-govt-set-to-vote-on-building-plan/00000190-6894-d747-add0-e8ddc0db0000</link><description>总理办公室去年宣布，鉴于成本高昂，正在考虑取消贝尔福官邸的翻修工程，转而建造新院落。然而最近，该办公室选择耗资数千万谢克尔对其进行翻修，同时也推进新大楼的建设</description><pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 11:39:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-could-get-two-new-residences-and-an-office-as-govt-set-to-vote-on-building-plan/00000190-6894-d747-add0-e8ddc0db0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列极右翼部长称，无法逃脱针对真主党的“尖锐、快速”战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/no-escape-from-sharp-quick-war-against-hezbollah-israeli-far-right-minister-says/00000190-687d-d747-add0-e8fd070e0000</link><description>以色列部长贝扎莱尔·斯莫特里奇也感谢特朗普在与拜登的总统辩论中拒绝支持巴勒斯坦国</description><pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 10:29:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/no-escape-from-sharp-quick-war-against-hezbollah-israeli-far-right-minister-says/00000190-687d-d747-add0-e8fd070e0000</guid></item><item><title>尽管威胁不断升级，伊朗并不急于与以色列发生直接冲突</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/despite-escalating-threats-iran-isnt-rushing-toward-a-direct-clash-with-israel/00000190-67f1-d499-a5bf-effffb170000</link><description>随着加沙战争的继续，伊朗继续进行心理战，威胁以色列和拜登政府不要对黎巴嫩真主党发动全面军事行动。但它没有宣布将直接参与此类活动</description><pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 08:29:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/despite-escalating-threats-iran-isnt-rushing-toward-a-direct-clash-with-israel/00000190-67f1-d499-a5bf-effffb170000</guid></item><item><title>拜登总统辩论惨败可能会诱使美国在中东的敌人考验他的决心</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/bidens-presidential-debate-fiasco-may-tempt-u-s-foes-in-the-mideast-to-test-his-resolve/00000190-6594-d0b3-a7d1-67dc5c3e0000</link><description>除了拜登疲倦的表现在民主党中激起前所未有的动荡外，美国的领导力危机预计还将在世界各地引发二次地震，尤其是在中东</description><pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 05:09:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/bidens-presidential-debate-fiasco-may-tempt-u-s-foes-in-the-mideast-to-test-his-resolve/00000190-6594-d0b3-a7d1-67dc5c3e0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡政府一致再次任命丹尼·达农为以色列下一任驻联合国特使</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-government-expected-to-re-appoint-danny-dannon-as-israels-next-envoy-to-un/00000190-6525-d747-add0-edfd99610000</link><description>利库德集团成员丹尼·达农将接替过去四年担任以色列驻联合国大使的吉拉德·埃尔丹。这将是达农第二次担任该职位，他于 2015 年至 2020 年间担任该职位</description><pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 03:00:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-government-expected-to-re-appoint-danny-dannon-as-israels-next-envoy-to-un/00000190-6525-d747-add0-edfd99610000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军称，早些时候在以色列北部发生的无人机爆炸事件造成 18 名以色列士兵受伤，其中一人重伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article-live/two-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-north-gaza-freed-hostages-urge-government-to-reach-deal/00000190-66f3-d90c-a7fc-77f73c5b0000</link><description>美国军方表示，在红海摧毁了三艘胡塞武装船只 ■ 伊斯兰圣战组织 Tul Karm 营的主要特工在以色列袭击中丧生 ■ 戈兰高地无人机爆炸造成 5 人受伤，其中一人伤势严重 ■ 梅图拉委员会：真主党导弹对房屋造成损害 ■ 报告加沙：周日有 22 人死亡；加沙城有针对性的袭击造成三人死亡</description><pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 02:29:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article-live/two-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-north-gaza-freed-hostages-urge-government-to-reach-deal/00000190-66f3-d90c-a7fc-77f73c5b0000</guid></item></channel></rss>